 ],
 "segments": [
  {
   "start": 0.0,
   "end": 3.32,
   "text": " There's a company that makes more money per employee than almost anyone on earth,"
  },
  {
   "start": 3.78,
   "end": 8.4,
   "text": " around 100 staff, billions in annual profit, and the entire business model is this."
  },
  {
   "start": 8.84,
   "end": 12.76,
   "text": " You give them a dollar, they hand you a token, and they keep the dollar, that's Tether,"
  },
  {
   "start": 12.98,
   "end": 14.08,
   "text": " and it's completely legal."
  },
  {
   "start": 14.58,
   "end": 17.46,
   "text": " Here's why it might be the most genius business model ever invented."
  },
  {
   "start": 17.86,
   "end": 20.06,
   "text": " Tether runs USDT, a stablecoin."
  },
  {
   "start": 20.54,
   "end": 23.44,
   "text": " One USDT is always meant to equal one US dollar."
  },
  {
   "start": 23.94,
   "end": 27.38,
   "text": " Crypto traders love it, it's a dollar that lives on the blockchain so they can"
  },
  {
   "start": 27.38,
   "end": 29.0,
   "text": " jump in and out of trades instantly."
  },
  {
   "start": 29.72,
   "end": 32.96,
   "text": " To get one, you hand Tether a real dollar and they mint you a token."
  },
  {
   "start": 33.36,
   "end": 36.98,
   "text": " Simple, but the magic isn't the token, it's what happens to your dollar."
  },
  {
   "start": 37.4,
   "end": 39.64,
   "text": " Because Tether doesn't just let your dollar sit in a drawer,"
  },
  {
   "start": 40.02,
   "end": 43.34,
   "text": " it takes all those billions in parks, the mostly in US treasury bills."
  },
  {
   "start": 43.86,
   "end": 48.02,
   "text": " Basically the safest loan on the planet, earning around 4-5% a year."
  },
  {
   "start": 48.46,
   "end": 50.64,
   "text": " And how much of that interest do they pass back to you?"
  },
  {
   "start": 50.98,
   "end": 51.68,
   "text": " The token holder?"
  },
  {
   "start": 52.12,
   "end": 52.44,
   "text": " Zero."
  },
  {
   "start": 52.78,
   "end": 55.98,
   "text": " You're holding a dollar that pays you nothing, and Tether keeps every cent of"
  },
  {
   "start": 55.98,
   "end": 56.3,
   "text": " the yield."
  },
  {
   "start": 56.72,
   "end": 57.6,
   "text": " Now multiply it."
  },
  {
   "start": 57.6,
   "end": 62.12,
   "text": " There's well over $100 billion of USDT out there, which means well over"
  },
  {
   "start": 62.12,
   "end": 65.28,
   "text": " $100 billion of other people's money working for Tether, for free."
  },
  {
   "start": 65.74,
   "end": 67.48,
   "text": " And normally, getting capital is expensive."
  },
  {
   "start": 67.74,
   "end": 71.52,
   "text": " A bank pays interest to its depositors, a company pays interest on its bonds,"
  },
  {
   "start": 72.1,
   "end": 73.12,
   "text": " everyone pays for money."
  },
  {
   "start": 73.58,
   "end": 74.18,
   "text": " Tether's cost?"
  },
  {
   "start": 74.62,
   "end": 74.78,
   "text": " Nothing."
  },
  {
   "start": 75.14,
   "end": 77.74,
   "text": " It's an interest-free loan from millions of users, and"
  },
  {
   "start": 77.74,
   "end": 79.4,
   "text": " it keeps 100% of the return."
  },
  {
   "start": 79.9,
   "end": 83.86,
   "text": " In 2024, the company reported around $13 billion in profit,"
  },
  {
   "start": 84.06,
   "end": 85.88,
   "text": " with a team you could fit in a single room."
  },
  {
   "start": 85.88,
   "end": 87.16,
   "text": " So what's the catch?"
  },
  {
   "start": 88.1,
   "end": 91.7,
   "text": " Trust, the whole thing holds up only as long as people believe every token is"
  },
  {
   "start": 91.7,
